metadata.name: ADAGIRLS HIDDEN
metadata.description: ADA’S World Pioneers is made up of 666 ADA brave girls. They are explorers and pioneers of new lands. The ADA world maps the current economic environment as well as the digital market. There will always be light, and darkness will eventually fade. They are not afraid of failure. ADA’S People are not afraid of the abyss. New lands will eventually appear. We will eventually go to the light.
